overview: On February 19th AAA Lucha Libre presents Rey de Reyes! The lineup has well over 7 matches and features the five-man Rey de Reyes 2022 match where contenders are - Psycho Clown vs Cibernetico vs Laredo Ki vs Luchadora Sorpresa vs Bandido. Who will become King of the Kings 2022?
title: AAA Rey de Reyes 2022
